sections.content:
WHEREFORE, Petitioner requests that this Court:

1. Dissolve the marriage between Petitioner and Respondent;

2. Award custody, parenting time, and child support as requested herein;

3. Equitably divide the marital property and debts between the parties;

4. Award spousal support/alimony as requested herein;

5. Grant the name change as requested herein;

6. Issue the restraining orders as requested herein;

7. Grant any other relief the Court deems just and proper under the circumstances.
